name: Hover
description:
The artwork shows a woman walking over a lake heading towards a fanciful yet realistic realm.
Inspired by women´s empowerment, the artwork represents its courage and braveness while heading into unknown and new challenges. The fact of the main character of this piece walks over the water could be interpreted as the capacity of humankind to get over obstacles along their way.

Landscape concept art. Digital illustration created with an extensive brush package and warm color palette. 

Phantom Illustrations X NFT Advisor. Edition 5/5
